@{b}GetGeneralPrefs@{ub}

    NAME

        GetGeneralPrefs - Read the current General settings

    SYNOPSIS

        GetGeneralPrefs STEM/A

    FUNCTION

        Read the current General settings.
        The settings will be written to the given stem variable.
        The following stem items are available:

            stem.fontsize  - Font size in pt
            stem.fontsize2 - Font size of level 2 in pt
            stem.fontsize3 - Font size of level 3 in pt
            stem.xdpi      - Display x dpi
            stem.ydpi      - Display y dpi

    INPUTS

        STEM - Name of a stem variable the settings items will be
               written to

    SEE ALSO
        @{"SetGeneralPrefs" link ARexxSetGeneralPrefs}

@endnode

